Governors elected under the platform of the ruling All Progressives Congress (APC) have acknowledged the motherly care and selfless support of the First Lady, Hajiya Aisha Buhari to the processes of managing challenges of governance in the country. The Governors under the ageis of Progressive Governors’ Forum (PGF) in a congratulatory message to mark the 50th birthday of the First Lady by their chairman Abubakar Bagudu of Kebbi felicitated with the President’s wife on her golden birthday celebration. The statement reads: “The Progressive Governors Forum (PGF) joins His Excellency, President Muhammadu Buhari, GCFR, his family and all Nigerians to celebrate Her Excellency Aisha Buhari on her Golden Age of 50. “We celebrate this special occasion and pray for more blessings and God’s guidance. “We wish to acknowledge and commend Her Excellency’s motherly care to the nation and in particular, your contributions to our successes through insightful and selfless support to the processes of managing challenges of governance in the country. “As First Lady, you have supported our development initiatives and always demonstrated keen interest towards ensuring that the change we promise Nigerians remained a shining light of our administration. “We rejoice with you and will always remain grateful for your guidance and support. “Congratulations and Happy Golden Birthday to Her Excellency.”